message.body: Are you back from your retreat?
Hey! We are still here, but heading out around 1pm! :)
That's awesome! Is there a sculpture garden? I saw those pics looks so nice!
No that place we drove to yesterday...it was about 40 minutes from where we're staying. It's called storm king art garden...it's so amazing there!
It's just like acres and acres of land with huge sculptures everywhere!
What you been up to this week??
So cool! It's been so busy this week.
You're the busiest person I know!
What's the thing you're going to at the rotunda?
I'm taking today off! Watching tv eating pancakes! I'm going to an art/sound opening. One of my colleagues has work
Nice! Sounds like such a good day! :)
